  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/21/nike-running-for-iphone-now-keeps-you-motivated-with-coaching/\"><img alt=\"Nike+ Running for iPhone with coach mode\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/5a17946f9c61745bca054d6f782c2264/nike-plus-running-coach.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n圣诞、新年马上就要到了，大吃特吃之外，也不要忘记锻炼减重啊。为了帮助大家更好地完成后面这个目标，Nike 适时地升级了自己的 iOS 版 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/nikeplus\">Nike+</a> Running 应用。在新版本中多出了 Nike+ Coach 教练模式，它可以根据使用者的锻炼目标和水平制定训练计划，无论是较为轻松的 5K 还是大运动量的马拉松都不在话下。最后，既然是教练的话一定会督促你认真锻炼，在用户偷懒时应用会发出提醒和健身窍门。当然，我们不能保证用了 Nike+ Running 后你的身材一定会变得更好，但它反正是免费的，试试也无妨啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/20/nike-running-for-iphone-now-keeps-you-motivated-with-coaching/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://9to5mac.com/2013/12/20/nike-running-iphone-app-gets-new-nike-coach-feature-w-daily-training-programs-coaching-tips/\" target=\"_blank\">9to5 Mac</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/app/nike+-running/id387771637?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/20/nike-running-for-iphone-now-keeps-you-motivated-with-coaching/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20793121/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/20/nike-running-for-iphone-now-keeps-you-motivated-with-coaching/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
